    {
      "id": "4.0",
      "step_order_index": 5,
      "assistant_prompt": "Perfect! Let's sharpen your niche by layering specificity.\n\nUse this structure:\n1. Problem you solve\n2. Problem + Who it's for\n3. Problem + Specific 'Who'\n4. Problem + Specific 'Who' + Domain area\n\n**Example:**\n1. Mental health\n2. Mental health for teenagers\n3. Mental health for anxious teenage girls\n4. Mental health for anxious teenage girls struggling with comparison\n\nShare your 4-layer niche for the audience you chose.\n\nAim for 4 bullet points following this structure.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "niche_layers",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "5.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5.0",
      "step_order_index": 6,
      "assistant_prompt": "Excellent. Now let's unpack why your audience hasn't solved their problem yet.\n\nList **at least 10 reasons** — internal, external, or motivational:\n• Internal belief (e.g., \"I'm not good enough\")\n• External blocker (e.g., \"I can't afford it\")\n• Motivation gap (e.g., \"I'll get to it eventually\")\n\nThese will become the raw ingredients of your offer.\n\nAim for 10+ bullet points.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "excuses_and_resistance",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "6.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6.0",
      "step_order_index": 7,
      "assistant_prompt": "Great list! Now for each reason, let's identify both **service** and **physical** solutions.\n\nI'll guide you through analyzing each excuse. For the first reason you listed, let's start with the **Service Solution**:\n\n**How do you make it better than existing solutions?**\n\nSelect all that apply and explain how:",
      "expected_inputs": [
        {
          "type": "multi_select",
          "options": ["Faster", "Easier", "Cheaper", "Better quality"]
        },
        {
          "type": "free_text",
          "label": "Explain how:"
        }
      ],
      "store_as": "reason_1.service.advantages",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "6.1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "6.1",
      "step_order_index": 7,
      "assistant_prompt": "For this service solution:\n\n**Why would they trust you?**",
      "expected_inputs": ["free_text"],
      "store_as": "reason_1.service.trust_factor",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "6.2"
        }
